00:24:04.800 --> 00:24:08.839
So that's a card that represents singular content items.

00:24:08.839 --> 00:24:11.959
You can put multiple cards on a page.

00:24:11.959 --> 00:24:14.319
You don't need to use the card content type.

00:24:14.319 --> 00:24:18.439
You can pull it out and you can use something like a grid.

00:24:18.439 --> 00:24:23.439
So if you want to represent more content in less space,

00:24:26.520 --> 00:24:28.719
you could choose a grid instead.

00:24:28.719 --> 00:24:33.520
So this represents a larger number of content.

00:24:33.520 --> 00:24:35.520
