The last content component is a table.

00:25:58.920 --> 00:26:03.920
So this is a set table of metadata.

00:26:04.479 --> 00:26:08.199
You get a name, a type, an owner, and last updated,

00:26:08.199 --> 00:26:13.199
and you get the mini content thumbnail images alongside.

