00:52:09.600 --> 00:52:13.679
now this will automatically get picked up, that change,

00:52:13.679 --> 00:52:17.239
every time the Connect polls Git for changes.

00:52:17.239 --> 00:52:20.040
I think that happens every 15 minutes or so,

00:52:20.040 --> 00:52:24.479
but Aaron, correct me if I'm wrong, if you know, on that.

00:52:24.479 --> 00:52:27.120
And if you are impatient

00:52:27.120 --> 00:52:28.919
and want to see the change right away,

00:52:28.919 --> 00:52:33.159
you can come to the info pane here and scroll down

00:52:33.159 --> 00:52:34.919
to where you can see that this content

00:52:34.919 --> 00:52:36.879
was generated from Git.

00:52:36.879 --> 00:52:38.959
So once you're back to the repository

00:52:38.959 --> 00:52:42.320
and it tells you which branch it's looking at

00:52:42.320 --> 00:52:45.360
and the directory within the repository,

00:52:45.360 --> 00:52:47.560
it's set to check for updates periodically.

00:52:47.560 --> 00:52:49.199
You can turn that behavior off

00:52:49.199 --> 00:52:51.399
