00:52:51.399 --> 00:52:55.239
but I mean, the point of this is to have it update periodically

00:52:55.239 --> 00:52:57.719
and watch that branch, so it's nice to have.

00:52:57.719 --> 00:52:59.959
If you want to see the change that reflected,

00:52:59.959 --> 00:53:02.439
it'll go out and look for that change.

00:53:02.439 --> 00:53:04.080
